  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If Slay the Spire had elemental factions to mix and match. You can approach the game like a traditional roguelite deck builder, opting for aggressive play styles. Alternatively, you can take a more methodical route, focusing on building up mana for long-term value or crafting unstoppable combos.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In BlueCloud Summit, unlike conventional roguelike deck builders, the emphasis is on freedom of exploration across a diverse hexagonal world. You have the choice to decide what to explore and how deeply, maximizing the opportunities available to you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.poster.avif?t=1744192830\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.webm?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.mp4?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t500+ Unique Cards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t6 element types enable countless unique builds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60+ relics to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tTest your build against 30+ unique enemies  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tRandomly generated maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decisions matter, strategizing and foresight can mean the difference between victory and death</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d7d29b21780ed53da4b57d7feafac58f.poster.avif?t=1744192830\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d7d29b21780ed53da4b57d7feafac58f.webm?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d7d29b21780ed53da4b57d7feafac58f.mp4?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If Slay the Spire had elemental factions to mix and match. You can approach the game like a traditional roguelite deck builder, opting for aggressive play styles. Alternatively, you can take a more methodical route, focusing on building up mana for long-term value or crafting unstoppable combos.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In BlueCloud Summit, unlike conventional roguelike deck builders, the emphasis is on freedom of exploration across a diverse hexagonal world. You have the choice to decide what to explore and how deeply, maximizing the opportunities available to you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.poster.avif?t=1744192830\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.webm?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446010/extras/d00e28999c9ac8d84564e2fb22d98213.mp4?t=1744192830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t500+ Unique Cards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t6 element types enable countless unique builds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60+ relics to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tTest your build against 30+ unique enemies  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tRandomly generated maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decisions matter, strategizing and foresight can mean the difference between victory and death</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinli